  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Grand Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/50px-Grand_Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/75px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/100px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Grand Maester</span><br />Ellendor</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Grand Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/50px-Grand_Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/75px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Grand_Maester.svg/100px-Grand_Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">The Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_167_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">167</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_171_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">171&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_258_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">258&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Calculation-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (Mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Ellendor</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> serving King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon V Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ellendor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ellendor was elected Grand Maester when he was close to 90 years old and was sent to serve the court of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon V Targaryen</a> to replace the late Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Kaeth\" title=\"Kaeth\">Kaeth</a>. Ellendor died within a year of his appointment and was succeeded by Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Merion\" title=\"Merion\">Merion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ellendor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Calculation-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Calculation_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Ellendor\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Ellendor</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Cersei VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kaeth\" title=\"Kaeth\">Kaeth</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_258_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">258&#160;AC</a>        <br /><s